  "prompt": "What is Roadrunner Technical Support?",
  "response": "Roadrunner Technical Support is a service designed to assist users with issues related to Roadrunner, an email service that was originally provided by Time Warner Cable and is now part of Spectrum. The technical support encompasses a range of services, including helping users with email setup, troubleshooting login issues, resolving email sending/receiving problems, configuring email clients, and addressing any security concerns like spam or hacking attempts.\n\nCustomers can typically access Roadrunner Technical Support through various channels such as phone support, online chat, or by visiting support pages on the Spectrum website. This support is crucial for maintaining uninterrupted email services and ensuring user queries and issues are resolved efficiently.",
